Finnair Looks to Cut Employee Costs Further, Kauppalehti Says

-- B y   D i a n a   b e n - A a r o n
-- 
2011-05-10T06:38:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/finnair-looks-to-cut-employee-costs-further-kauppalehti-says.html
Finnair Oyj (FIA1S) ,  Finland ’s biggest
airline, is still looking to cut personnel costs, the Finnish
business daily Kauppalehti reported, citing Chairman Harri
Sailas.    “I believe the employees understand that Finnair is
seeking cheaper solutions through various means,” Sailas said
according to Kauppalehti. He didn’t rule out hiring more workers
abroad, the newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
